<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Absolutely, this is suitable. It is an open and honest account that reflects a challenging attitude and a sense of inquiry. It is unflinching and all <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Absolutely, this is suitable. It is an open and honest account that reflects a challenging attitude and a sense of inquiry. It is unflinching and all the better for it. My 13 year old daughter loved it, and I was delighted when she said she wanted to read it. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
